dapat gawin ito nang walang ingat.

819
01:01:37,399 --> 01:01:38,692
Kailangan mo ng mahusay na kasanayan.

820
01:02:01,924 --> 01:02:03,133
Tingnan mo.

821
01:02:04,176 --> 01:02:06,595
Dito ka lang, mahuhulog ka...

822
01:02:11,767 --> 01:02:12,809
Pababa.

823
01:02:14,728 --> 01:02:16,104
Hindi mo 'yan matatalo.

824
01:02:16,813 --> 01:02:18,106
Masasabi ko na ang makinang ito ng crane

825
01:02:18,190 --> 01:02:21,151
